Class SHA384

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class SHA384
extends SHA64bit
    This class implements the SHA-384 message digest algorithm recently proposed by NIST. Note that SHA-384 is essentially a truncated SHA-512, which means it has the same runtime performance and memory usage.
